ygData.msgSnippet: Ooi Ah Rune, Dark Flame here, ya UO kakis, remember? ;)  I retired from tDw GM post liao, now a semi-retired elder in the guild and spend my time playing EQ
ygData.messageBody:
Ooi Ah Rune, Dark Flame here, ya UO kakis, remember? ;) I retired from tDw
GM post liao, now a semi-retired elder in the guild and spend my time
playing EQ instead.
We are based mainly at Freeport. Maybe u can meet Zanderion, who is at
Felwithe, take a boat to join us. We are now with an egyptian guild called
Qui Hoon Hai (?), u can join us for easy communication. It's much
comfortable to be a member instead of a GM. Now I just need to help
recruiting, no need to manage guild work - more time for enjoyment, hehe.

Ziltus, High-Elf Wizard (aka Dark Flame from UO)
